<item>
            <title>[PIG-3608] ClassCastException when looking up a value from AvroMapWrapper using a Utf8 key</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3608</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One got the following exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
java.lang.ClassCastException: org.apache.avro.util.Utf8 incompatible with java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; 
    at org.apache.pig.impl.util.avro.AvroMapWrapper.get(AvroMapWrapper.java:80)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is related to the change by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3420&quot; title=&quot;Failed to retrieve map values from data loaded by AvroStorage&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3420&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3420&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12682759">PIG-3608</key>
